3
00:00:05.055 --> 00:00:09.222
as the other hand is holding this little clicker here, okay?

4
00:00:10.161 --> 00:00:13.379
If I have to hold a microphone in one hand,

5
00:00:13.379 --> 00:00:15.817
then I make sure it's close enough to my mouth,

6
00:00:15.817 --> 00:00:16.943
make sure you do that, right.

7
00:00:16.943 --> 00:00:18.169
I've actually made a lot of mistakes

8
00:00:18.169 --> 00:00:19.889
in speeches where it's too far away.

9
00:00:19.889 --> 00:00:21.786
Right, make sure it's up here, okay?

10
